{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":754,"text":"Growing up in Taiwan"},{"time":2810,"text":"as the daughter of a calligrapher,"},{"time":4422,"text":"one of my most treasured memories"},{"time":6790,"text":"was my mother showing me the beauty, the shape"},{"time":9883,"text":"and the form of Chinese characters."},{"time":12516,"text":"Ever since then, I was fascinated"},{"time":15023,"text":"by this incredible language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17685,"text":"But to an outsider, it seems to be"},{"time":20420,"text":"as impenetrable as the Great Wall of China."},{"time":23929,"text":"Over the past few years, I've been wondering"},{"time":26304,"text":"if I can break down this wall,"},{"time":28356,"text":"so anyone who wants to understand and appreciate"},{"time":30950,"text":"the beauty of this sophisticated language could do so."},{"time":34858,"text":"I started thinking about how a new, fast method"},{"time":39170,"text":"of learning Chinese might be useful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42018,"text":"Since the age of five, I started to learn how to draw"},{"time":46004,"text":"every single stroke for each character"},{"time":49009,"text":"in the correct sequence."},{"time":51553,"text":"I learned new characters every day"},{"time":53610,"text":"during the course of the next 15 years."},{"time":56337,"text":"Since we only have five minutes,"},{"time":58457,"text":"it's better that we have a fast and simpler way."},{"time":62092,"text":"A Chinese scholar would understand 20,000 characters."},{"time":65617,"text":"You only need 1,000 to understand the basic literacy."},{"time":70729,"text":"The top 200 will allow you to comprehend"},{"time":74745,"text":"40 percent of basic literature --"},{"time":77641,"text":"enough to read road signs, restaurant menus,"},{"time":80517,"text":"to understand the basic idea of the web pages"},{"time":83521,"text":"or the newspapers."},{"time":85460,"text":"Today I'm going to start with eight"},{"time":87659,"text":"to show you how the method works."},{"time":89551,"text":"You are ready?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91472,"text":"Open your mouth as wide as possible"},{"time":94155,"text":"until it's square."},{"time":96201,"text":"You get a mouth."},{"time":98883,"text":"This is a person going for a walk."},{"time":101971,"text":"Person."},{"time":105102,"text":"If the shape of the fire is a person"},{"time":107811,"text":"with two arms on both sides,"},{"time":110081,"text":"as if she was yelling frantically,"},{"time":112251,"text":"\"Help! I'm on fire!\" --"},{"time":115804,"text":"This symbol actually is originally from the shape of the flame,"},{"time":119971,"text":"but I like to think that way. Whichever works for you."},{"time":123784,"text":"This is a tree."},{"time":126043,"text":"Tree."},{"time":128141,"text":"This is a mountain."},{"time":132566,"text":"The sun."},{"time":137458,"text":"The moon."},{"time":142112,"text":"The symbol of the door"},{"time":144087,"text":"looks like a pair of saloon doors in the wild west."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149793,"text":"I call these eight characters radicals."},{"time":153531,"text":"They are the building blocks"},{"time":155297,"text":"for you to create lots more characters."},{"time":159427,"text":"A person."},{"time":161165,"text":"If someone walks behind, that is \"to follow.\""},{"time":165433,"text":"As the old saying goes,"},{"time":167561,"text":"two is company, three is a crowd."},{"time":171287,"text":"If a person stretched their arms wide,"},{"time":174202,"text":"this person is saying, \"It was this big.\""},{"time":178849,"text":"The person inside the mouth, the person is trapped."},{"time":182697,"text":"He's a prisoner, just like Jonah inside the whale."},{"time":188543,"text":"One tree is a tree. Two trees together, we have the woods."},{"time":192037,"text":"Three trees together, we create the forest."},{"time":195593,"text":"Put a plank underneath the tree, we have the foundation."},{"time":199665,"text":"Put a mouth on the top of the tree, that's \"idiot.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":203800,"text":"Easy to remember,"},{"time":205881,"text":"since a talking tree is pretty idiotic."},{"time":210823,"text":"Remember fire?"},{"time":212865,"text":"Two fires together, I get really hot."},{"time":215526,"text":"Three fires together, that's a lot of flames."},{"time":218385,"text":"Set the fire underneath the two trees, it's burning."},{"time":222986,"text":"For us, the sun is the source of prosperity."},{"time":226078,"text":"Two suns together, prosperous."},{"time":228257,"text":"Three together, that's sparkles."},{"time":230615,"text":"Put the sun and the moon shining together,"},{"time":232636,"text":"it's brightness."},{"time":233944,"text":"It also means tomorrow, after a day and a night."},{"time":238169,"text":"The sun is coming up above the horizon. Sunrise."},{"time":242652,"text":"A door. Put a plank inside the door,"},{"time":245755,"text":"it's a door bolt."},{"time":247812,"text":"Put a mouth inside the door, asking questions."},{"time":250776,"text":"Knock knock. Is anyone home?"},{"time":254107,"text":"This person is sneaking out of a door,"},{"time":256995,"text":"escaping, evading."},{"time":259827,"text":"On the left, we have a woman."},{"time":261980,"text":"Two women together, they have an argument."},{"time":264142,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":266275,"text":"Three women together, be careful, it's adultery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272793,"text":"So we have gone through almost 30 characters."},{"time":276302,"text":"By using this method, the first eight radicals"},{"time":279639,"text":"will allow you to build 32."},{"time":281640,"text":"The next group of eight characters"},{"time":283403,"text":"will build an extra 32."},{"time":285595,"text":"So with very little effort,"},{"time":287897,"text":"you will be able to learn a couple hundred characters,"},{"time":290163,"text":"which is the same as a Chinese eight-year-old."},{"time":292715,"text":"So after we know the characters, we start building phrases."},{"time":296262,"text":"For example, the mountain and the fire together,"},{"time":298959,"text":"we have fire mountain. It's a volcano."},{"time":301887,"text":"We know Japan is the land of the rising sun."},{"time":305207,"text":"This is a sun placed with the origin,"},{"time":308625,"text":"because Japan lies to the east of China."},{"time":311752,"text":"So a sun, origin together, we build Japan."},{"time":315642,"text":"A person behind Japan, what do we get?"},{"time":318600,"text":"A Japanese person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321702,"text":"The character on the left is two mountains"},{"time":324503,"text":"stacked on top of each other."},{"time":326610,"text":"In ancient China, that means in exile,"},{"time":329827,"text":"because Chinese emperors, they put their political enemies"},{"time":332265,"text":"in exile beyond mountains."},{"time":334636,"text":"Nowadays, exile has turned into getting out."},{"time":339647,"text":"A mouth which tells you where to get out"},{"time":342218,"text":"is an exit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344146,"text":"This is a slide to remind me that I should stop talking"},{"time":347787,"text":"and get off of the stage. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349670,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}